"      Chobanian AV, Bakris GL, Black HR, et al, &ldquo;The Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation, and Treatment of High Blood Pressure: The JNC 7 report,&rdquo;",
"      <i>",
"       JAMA",
"      </i>",
"      , 2003, 289(19):2560-72.",
"      <span class=\"pubmed-id\">",
"       [PubMed",
"       <a href=\"UTD.htm?4/53/4949/abstract-text/12748199/pubmed\" id=\"12748199\" target=\"_blank\">",
"        12748199",
